{"word":"σπουδαίως","slug":"σπουδαίως","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b><el>σπουδαίως</el></b> [<el><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:σπουδαῖος\">σπουδαῖος</a></el>] <a class=\"G\" href=\"S:✎ adv.\">adv.</a> ‘with earnest attention’, <b>urgently, with concern <a href='B:490 7:4'>Lk 7:4</a>; eagerly <a href='B:620 1:17'>2 Ti 1:17</a>; with concern for need <a href='B:630 3:13'>Tit 3:13</a>;</b> <a class=\"G\" href=\"S:✎ comp.\">comp.</a> <el>σπουδαιοτέρως</el> <b>with all the more sense of urgency <a href='B:570 2:28'>Phil 2:28</a>;</b> <el>σπουδαιότερον</el> <b>very eagerly <a href='B:620 1:17'>2 Ti 1:17</a> <a class=\"G\" href=\"S:✎ v.l.\">v.l.</a></b> <center id=\"nav_bottom\"> <a id=\"left_arrow\" href=\"S:σπουδαῖος\">&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;</a> <a id=\"bottom_home\" href=\"S:#1.Table of Contents\">&emsp;&emsp;</a> <a id=\"right_arrow\" href=\"S:σπουδή\">&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;</a> </center> "}]}